native.query:
WITH merchants_last_order as (SELECT max(id) as id
    FROM "l0_timon"."orders"
    GROUP BY merchant_id)

SELECT
    merchant_id,
    CASE
        WHEN
        /* Check for valid IPv4: four groups of 0-255 */
            cast(raw_before.platform.name as text) ~ 
            '^(25[0-5]|2[0-4]\d|[01]?\d?\d)(\.(25[0-5]|2[0-4]\d|[01]?\d?\d)){3}$' OR 
        /* Check for a (simplified) IPv6 pattern */
            cast(raw_before.platform.name as text) ~ 
            '^([0-9A-Fa-f]{1,4}:){7}[0-9A-Fa-f]{1,4}$' OR 
            cast(raw_before.platform.name as text) ~* '.*logicommerce.*'
            
        THEN 'Logicommerce'
        
        WHEN raw_before.platform.name = 'REPLACE WITH CORRECT VALUE BEFORE QA' THEN 'Vitaldent'
        WHEN raw_before.platform.name = 'Shopify Gateway' THEN 'Shopify'
        
        /* If the value is one of these known platforms, return it as is */
        WHEN raw_before.platform.name IN ('Magento', 'PrestaShop', 'WooCommerce', 'Velfix', 'Wix', 'BigCommerce', 'Drupal', 'OpenCart', 'Odoo', 'Shopify', 'Shenzi', 'InstoreSales', 'Atnova Shop', 'Dataweb', 'OsCommerce')
        THEN raw_before.platform.name
        
        /* Otherwise, return "Other" */
        ELSE 'Custom (API)'
    END AS platform
FROM
    "l0_timon"."orders" o 
    LEFT JOIN merchants_last_order A on A.id=o.id

SELECT 
    DATE_TRUNC('month',confirmed_at) AS month,
    ecommerce,
    COUNT(DISTINCT "si_reference") AS merchant_count,
    sum(current_order_value) as current_order_value
FROM 
    "l2_partnerships"."partnerships"
WHERE ecommerce != 'other'

GROUP BY 
    month,
    ecommerce
ORDER BY 
    month;

SELECT
  TO_CHAR(CURRENT_DATE, 'YYYY') AS "date"
FROM
  "l2_cro"."financials_data"
LIMIT 1;

    SELECT
      order_id
    FROM
      l0_simba.payment_plan_configurations

    WHERE

  min(pu.created_at) first_changed_on

            )
          )
          AND ole.id > 284350000
          AND ppc."late_fee_plan_configuration_name" = 'default_20241010'

    FROM

    WHERE
